Hi Alice,

Thank you for the detailed bug report and the HAR file you attached.

We have reproduced the issue in Firefox 121 when the table has more than
500 rows. The root cause is a Content-Disposition header being stripped
by Firefox's stricter CSP handling.

A fix is scheduled for the next release (2.9.3) on January 22nd. In the
meantime you can use the workaround: hold Shift while clicking Export to
trigger a direct download instead of the blob URL.

Sorry for the inconvenience.

Kind regards,
